    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and makes for a reliable, well-maintained choice for everyday drivers. The exterior presents nicely \u2014 you'll notice only minor surface scuffs and light wear consistent with normal use, nothing that detracts significantly from its overall appearance. The interior is clean and functional, with typical signs of regular use but no major damage or excessive wear. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been properly maintained, giving the next owner a dependable platform to work from. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and electrical \u2014 are in good working order. This is a straightforward, honest offering for a buyer looking for solid transportation without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 31000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
